Reasoning: 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper deals with the control problem of a platoon of vehicles, which falls under the scope of systems and control. 
- cs.RO (Robotics): The paper includes a real-time experiment conducted with mobile robots, indicating that it belongs to the robotics field. 
- cs.MA (Multiagent Systems): The platoon of vehicles can be considered as a multiagent system, where each vehicle acts as an agent and interacts with its neighboring agents. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): Although the paper does not explicitly mention the use of AI techniques, the control protocols proposed in the paper can be considered as intelligent decision-making algorithms. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering): The paper does not focus on software engineering, but it may involve software implementation of the proposed control protocols.
